snippet.title: Caught on camera: Transgender woman assaulted on NYC subway

localized.description:
A transgender woman named Pearl Love filmed a stranger on a New York City subway verbally and apparently physically assaulting her as passengers stood by silently. The incident reportedly occurred on April 28 between 4:30-4:45 pm when she was changed from the 6 train to the 4 express train at 125 St station.

The nearly two-minute long video, posted to Love’s Facebook page on May 2, shows an unknown woman repeatedly shouting racial and transphobic slurs to Love while sitting down across the aisle from her.
